Company Overview of The Scotts Company LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
The Scotts Company LLC manufactures, markets, and supplies products for lawn and garden care. It also manufactures and markets professional golf course turf care products. The company offers products for professional horticulture, consumer herbicides, fertilizer line, and plant fertilizers. It provides its products in the United States, France, Germany, the United Kingdom, and Europe. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in Marysville, Ohio. The Scotts Company LLC operates as a subsidiary of The Scotts Miracle-Gro Company.


