Scotts is a global leader in growing media and plant protection. It remains highly reliant on the US market, however this market will lead growth in garden care going forward which presents an opportunity for Scotts. Recent bolt-on acquisitions offer further potential to grow market share beyond the Scotts, Miracle-Gro and Ortho brands. 

